        <h2>What's New in 0.5.141</h2>
        <h3>Improvements</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Cmd+Shift+R now supports multiple selections</strong> &mdash; shift-select several samples, then Cmd+Shift+R to re-extract all of them from random positions in their original sources at once</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="source">Build 1202 &middot; <a href="https://github.com/danielraffel/PlunderTube/commit/8dae2d30">8dae2d30</a> on main</p>
